From David Brooks Subject Re XV author is on vacation till May or so writes For all those people flaming John Bradley the author of xv he's on vacation till May or I don't remember Maybe we all should slow down and wait to hear his side wrt copyrights fees While I have respect for John's ability and integrity I really regret his leaving just after a major release or more accurately making the release just before leaving Several of us are having problems with xv and in particular I have issues with all the fixes that have so far been made to the Imakefiles and Without John to adjudicate and everybody posting fixes that work for them chaos is inevitable let's hope it is John Guile Skywalker Brooks using his Dad's account